post_text:
Winterim is a great opportunity for APA students to participate in experiential learning in the Arts, Humanities, Science and Tech, History and Culture, and/or Fitness and Life Skills. We hope each student grows from their classes and has stories to share with family and friends for years to come.

APA extends a HUGE THANKS to all students, parents, and staff for making Winterim 2019 a great success!

@apawinterim @winterim @aparocks @apastudents @americanpreputah

