In our K-6 Classrooms, students eat lunch in their classrooms. During lunch "chew time" our instructors and parent volunteers read books to the students. Students at Draper 2 had the opportunity to visit Mrs. Foster's 2nd grade classroom where Ms. Nield was reading from "Charlie and the Chocolate Factory". What a great way to eat lunch and what a great book to hear during the class chew time.

#americanprep #apapositive #charterschool #2018openenrollment #americanpreparatoryacademy
